    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> PRG:TWoVHD</p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 150 gp; <b>Weight</b> -</p>\r\n<p>Drinking the cold, oily draught in this vial suppresses the effects of the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Light-Sensitivity-Ex-\">light sensitivity</a> racial trait for 10 minutes. Additionally, 1 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/featured-races/arg-dhampir#Sunlight-Syndrome\">sunlight syndrome</a> point is removed, if the drinker has any. Essence of night can remove only 1 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/featured-races/arg-dhampir#Sunlight-Syndrome\">sunlight syndrome</a> point per day, no matter how many flasks a character might drink.</p>\r\n<p>Essence of night is an alchemical item with a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> DC of 25.</p>\r\n",
